You may recall that she has allowed herself

91
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:44,850
four weekends for this project.

92
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:47,460
In doing so she has identified the amount of time

93
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:49,980
it will take her to complete the project.

94
00:03:49,980 --> 00:03:51,840
Before compiling the actual schedule

95
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:55,270
it would be advisable to follow the scheduling process.

